clue: "Square R1 Left L1 Circle" initially nets very large amount
explanation: It may look a bit like a cheat code, but there's a bit more going on here... In cryptic crosswordese, "square" often implies T (as in T-square). Then we've got RI (R1), L (Left), LI (L1), O (Circle), and N (initially NETS). All in all we've got TRILLION, a very large amount.
